data.description: Easy access to I-4 and downtown Lakeland.  Take a look at this home with 2 bedrooms, bath and bonus area for 3rd bedroom or office (No closet).  Roof and A.C was replaced in 2021 and Water Heater in 2024, Matching LG appliances including washer and dryer. Stone accents in living room features electric fireplace and room for your flat screen TV.  Dedicated Laundry room with washer and dryer.  Updated kitchen with 42 Inch expresso cabinets, granite countertops and tile floors throughout. Partially fenced back yard with slab ready for a shed or patio.  Immediate occupancy available.
